## Component Conventions

### Functional Components Only

Always use functional components with hooks. Never class components.

### State Management

- Local state with `useState` / `useReducer` inside components.
- Shared state (messages, streaming status) lives in `useSSEChat` and is passed as props.
- No global state library (no Redux, Zustand, etc.) in the MVP.

### Loading and Error States

- Every async operation has a loading and error state.
- Show errors as inline red text (`text-red-400`) within the component, not as modal dialogs.
- Use a Tailwind spinner (`animate-spin`) while loading, not a separate library.

### Accessibility

- Include `aria-label` on icon-only buttons (e.g., the send button).
- Use semantic HTML: `<main>`, `<aside>`, `<section>`, `<button>` (not `<div onClick>`).
- Ensure keyboard navigation works (Tab to input, Enter to send).

