## Environment Variables

| Variable | Description | Example |
| --- | --- | --- |
| `VITE_API_URL` | FastAPI backend base URL | `http://localhost:8000` |
| `VITE_DEFAULT_USER_ID` | Dev user ID for local testing | `dev_user_001` |

All Vite env vars must be prefixed with `VITE_` to be exposed to the browser bundle.

