## Build and Deployment

- Production build: `npm run build` outputs to `frontend/dist/`.
- The `dist/` folder is served as static files by a Nginx container or directly from Cloud Storage + CDN.
- The `VITE_API_URL` is baked into the bundle at build time — set it correctly in the CD pipeline.
